rep_input: Clinically, what are the on-label points I should know about Trodelvy in HR+/HER2- after prior CDK4/6?
model_output: Trodelvy is indicated for adults with unresectable or metastatic HR+/HER2- breast cancer who have received endocrine therapy and at least two prior systemic therapies, including a CDK4/6 inhibitor. Please review the EMA SmPC for full details and send me the latest version by email.
